metadata.name: ARIES
metadata.description:
Symbolized by the Ram, this Fire Sign is known to be competitive, energetic, fearless, yet impulsive. As the sign is ruled by Mars, a burning desire represented by the color red is often depicted alongside Aries.

Reinhardt chose Obianibeli Esu – a goddess in her own right born in the cusp of Aries-Taurus. As she blazes through her kingdom of crimson (created through generative art), the Aries Goddess eliminates all fear as she soars into her freedom.

Muse: Obianibeli Esu
Fashion: House of Puglielli, Usama Ishtay, Nigel Crow – all from The Archives & Showroom
VFX Make Up: Apple Molita
